This is my home directory. There are many like it, but this one is mine.
My home directory is my best friend. It is my life. I must master it as I must master my life.
My home directory, without me, is useless. Without my home directory, I am useless.

---

Quick setup: (copy-paste to terminal)

git clone --no-checkout git@github.com:bukzor/dotfiles.git  tmp-dotfiles
mv tmp-dotfiles/.git .
rmdir tmp-dotfiles
git checkout  .
